text: Cagalah Yallal dirab ginnaasittam yeemenek lakal koroosanni qangarat yaabe numu, toysa woo numul Yallih Naqbi yan, koroosanni qangarat yaabankeh dirkisen numuy iimaanat lubbi satta kak iyyay rabi meesih teetit yaabe akke waytek, kinnih immay koroosanni qangarat lubbi satta kak axcuk yaabe numul, toysa too maral Yallih naqbi yaniih akeeral kaxxa digaala lon
